DESCRIPTION
===========

* this sumorobot platform for Arduino is developed for young programmers
* this library can be used to control 2 servo motors and 2 distance + 3 light sensors
* schematics folder contains the Arduino shield schematics
* there is no instructions to build a body for the sumorobot


INSTALLATION
============

Steps:
1) copy Sumorobot into your arduino libraries folder and restart arduino
2) check out the documentation https://github.com/silps/sumoino/raw/master/documentation/Sumorobot2012_student.pdf
3) write some code xD (tip: see examples "Drive_EN", "Avoid_EN", "Opponent_EN")

Commands:
# this will install latest arduino and the Sumorobot library
# make sure that you will get arduino 1.0
sudo apt-get update && sudo apt-get install arduino && arduino
cd /var/tmp && git clone http://github.com/silps/sumoino.git
sudo cp -R sumoino/Sumorobot /usr/share/arduino/libraries


